name: Trippy Waterfall 👾🌊🔵
description: “Andre 3000- prototype”____  Complex simplicity ____  Alienated away from 2020 ____  Not many can escape Area 51 👽 ____  Enemies often situated in plain sight ____  Playing both sides ____  Lies and close ties like our relationship w/the sun ____  Amused by carbon copies of what use to be ____  Like fruit in grocery stores ____  Or even you and me ____  “Are you a true human?” she asked ____  Reflecting on a path that was bestowed ____ I said, “No, not like what you’ve seen”...
